   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The 4th year, Pharmouthi, from Tothoes and Palamounis, sitologoi of the grain-store in external districts. Grain received on the 21st from the produce of the said year : measured into the granary at Alabanthis for that village, for seed 14 artabas of wheat, for rent 449 1/2 1/3 art. of pure wheat, for loss in cleansing 9 1/3 1/12 art., fee for sifting 4 2/3 art., making 14 1/12 art., total 463 1/2 1/3 1/12 art.</ab>
         </div>
